50|$|<b>Clark</b> <b>Atlanta's</b> Center for Functional Nanoscale Measures (CFNM) has {{produced}} more black Ph.D.s in Nanoscale Science than any HBCU in the nation.|$|R
50|$|Amanda Davis {{graduated}} <b>Clark</b> College in <b>Atlanta,</b> Georgia as a Magna cum Laude.|$|R
